content.rendered: Tingkatkan sistem keamanan bangunan dengan memasang Honeywell HEW2PER2. Kamera CCTV Honeywell HEW2PER2 sangat efektif dalam menaga keamanan rumah / kantor / gedung / dlsb. Jenis kamera Honeywell type HEW2PER2 memiliki spesifikasi:1/2.8” 2 MP progressive scan imager 1920 x 1080 resolution 2.7-13.5mm MFZ lens F1.4 True day/night (IR-cut filter) Wide Dynamic Range up to 120 dB Low-light performance down to 0.05 lux (color) or 0 lux with IR LEDs on Up to 164 ft (50 m) IR illumination, depending on scene reflectance H.265 Smart Codec Triple stream support Support up to 128GB Micro SDHC card class 10 PoE (802.3af) or 12 VDC support Plug-and-play compatible with Honeywell Performance Series Embedded NVRs IP66 -rated housing
